## 六、index_search.html 标准结构

**必须用 `<fieldset>` + `<legend>` 包裹搜索内容：**

```html
<form class="layui-form layui-form-pane form-search" action="{:sysuri()}" onsubmit="return false" method="get" autocomplete="off">
    <fieldset>
        <legend>{:lang('条件搜索')}</legend>

        <div class="layui-form-item layui-inline">
            <label class="layui-form-label">{:lang('关键词')}</label>
            <div class="layui-input-inline">
                <input name="name" value="{$get.name|default=''}" placeholder="{:lang('请输入关键词')}" class="layui-input">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="layui-form-item layui-inline">
            <button class="layui-btn layui-btn-primary"><i class="layui-icon">&#xe615;</i> {:lang('搜 索')}</button>
        </div>
    </fieldset>
</form>
```

