## 八、form.html 标准结构

弹窗表单不继承，直接写完整 HTML：

```html
<form action="{:sysuri()}" method="post" data-auto="true" class="layui-form layui-card" data-table-id="XxxTable">
    <div class="layui-card-body padding-left-40">

        <fieldset class="layui-bg-gray">
            <legend><b class="layui-badge think-bg-violet">{:lang('基本信息')}</b></legend>
            <div class="layui-row layui-col-space15">

                <div class="layui-col-xs6">
                    <label class="block relative">
                        <span class="help-label"><b>{:lang('名称')}</b>Name</span>
                        <input name="name" value='{$vo.name|default=""}' required vali-name="{:lang('名称')}" class="layui-input">
                        <span class="help-block color-desc">{:lang('说明文字')}</span>
                    </label>
                </div>

            </div>
        </fieldset>

    </div>

    <div class="hr-line-dashed"></div>
    {notempty name='vo.id'}<input type='hidden' value='{$vo.id}' name='id' />{/notempty}

    <div class="layui-form-item text-center">
        <button class="layui-btn" type='submit'>{:lang('保存数据')}</button>
        <button class="layui-btn layui-btn-danger" type='button' data-confirm="{:lang('确定要取消编辑吗？')}" data-close>{:lang('取消编辑')}</button>
    </div>
</form>
```

